     H            Y/                                    1
      ***** GDGR1L ***********************************
      *     GET ORDER NUM, SEIH
      *     LEC                        2016/07/06
      ************************************************
     FAGDPL11 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAAPPL05 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAKBPL06 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAANPL05 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
      * System Date(8 DIGITS)
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80WSDATE
     I                                        1   40WSYYYY
     I                                        5   60WSMM
     I                                        7   80WSDD
     I                                        3   4 YY
     I                                        5   6 MM
      * Order number
     I                                        1   6 ODER
     I                                        1   2 YY@ORD
     I                                        3   4 MM@ORD
     I                                        5   6 SQ@ORD
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PZETI   4
     C                     PARM           PODER   6
     C                     PARM           PSEIH   1
     C                     PARM           PRENB   4
      *
      * blank out parameters
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   PODER
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    PSEIH
     C                     MOVE '0000'    PRENB
      *
      * Get Order Number
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     WSDATE
      *
     C           AGDP11    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           WSYYYY
     C                     KFLD           WSMM
      *
     C           AGDP11    CHAINAGDPL11              50
     C           *IN50     DOWEQ*OFF
      *
     C                     ADD  1         SEQ#    20
     C           F8KADD    IFEQ WSDD
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           AGDP11    READEAGDPL11                  50
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVE YY        YY@ORD
     C                     MOVE MM        MM@ORD
     C                     MOVE SEQ#      SQ@ORD
     C                     MOVE ODER      PODER
      *
      * Get Product Code (SEIH)
      *
      *  Find Absolute Id (ZETI)....
      *  Check for it in COMPLETION PRODUCT KANBAN M/F
      *
     C           AAPL05    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           PZETI
      *
     C           AAPL05    CHAINAAPPL05              50
     C           *IN50     DOWEQ*OFF
      *
     C           L5SKJY    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE '0'       PSEIH
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           AAPL05    READEAAPPL05                  50
     C                     ENDDO
      *
      *  If ZETI not found,
      *  Check for it in COMPONENTS KANBAN M/F
      *
     C           PSEIH     IFEQ *BLANK
      *
     C           AKBL06    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           PZETI
      *
     C           AKBL06    CHAINAKBPL06              50
     C           *IN50     DOWEQ*OFF
      *
     C           L1SKJY    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE '3'       PSEIH
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           AKBL06    READEAKBPL06                  50
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      *  If ZETI still not found,
      *  Check for it in HALF-FINISHED GOODS KANBAN M/F
      *
     C           PSEIH     IFEQ *BLANK
      *
     C           AANL05    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           PZETI
      *
     C           AANL05    CHAINAANPL05              50
     C           *IN50     DOWEQ*OFF
      *
     C           L7SKJY    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE '6'       PSEIH
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           AANL05    READEAANPL05                  50
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
